---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title:
description: "Essays, op-eds, and reporting on internet culture, digital identity, and the creator economy."
---

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div class="card hero-card">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="dot"></span> A home for thoughtful takes on digital life</div>
      <h2>Make sense of the <span>internet</span> you live in.</h2>
      <p>
        {{ site.title }} publishes essays, op-eds, and reporting on internet culture — from algorithms and aesthetics
        to creator economy drama and the way online life reshapes identity, money, and relationships.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn" href="/topics/">Explore topics</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/submit/">Submit a pitch</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="card side" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="mini">
        <h3>What we publish</h3>
        <p>Essays • Op-eds • Creator economy • Trend analysis • Platform power • Digital identity</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mini">
        <h3>Our editorial vibe</h3>
        <p>Edgy-smart, readable, and from-the-inside. Not a recap site — a meaning-making site.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mini">
        <h3>Want to write?</h3>
        <p>We love sharp angles, lived experience, and light reporting. Submit below.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="section-title">
    <div>
      <h3>Latest</h3>
      <p>Fresh essays (sample posts — edit in the CMS after setup)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="navlinks">
      <span class="tag accent">Internet Culture</span>
      <span class="tag cyan">Creator Economy</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">
    {% for post in collections.posts | slice(0,6) %}
      <article class="card post">
        <div class="meta">
          <span class="tag {% if post.data.type == 'Op-ed' %}accent{% endif %}{% if post.data.type == 'Analysis' %}cyan{% endif %}">{{ post.data.type }}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{{ post.data.readingTime }}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{{ post.data.author }}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        </div>
        <h4><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h4>
        <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="card wide">
    <div>
      <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">The Sunday Signal</h3>
      <p style="margin:0; color:var(--muted)">One email a week: our best essays + the internet story everyone will be talking about.</p>
      <div class="hr"></div>
      <p class="hint" style="margin:0">
        Newsletter provider hookup: paste your Beehiiv / ConvertKit / Mailchimp embed code into <strong>/newsletter/</strong>.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:12px">
        <a class="btn" href="/newsletter/">Newsletter setup</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/submit/">Write for us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mini">
      <h3>What you’ll get</h3>
      <p>
        • 5-minute read list<br>
        • One sharp op-ed<br>
        • A trend decoded<br>
        • Tools + links worth saving
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
